decks.notes: This deck focuses on utilizing Yorion, Sky Nomad as a companion to create a more control-centric strategy. The deck features a variety of cards that offer removal, card advantage, and powerful creatures to control the game. With a mix of enchantments like Leyline Binding and powerful creatures like Elesh Norn, Mother of Machines, the deck aims to disrupt opponents while setting up its own win conditions. The mana base is diverse to support the deck's multi-color requirements and ensure consistency in casting spells.
